dct_description_sm: prepared by the British Government's Ministry of Overseas Development (Directorate of Overseas Surveys) under the Special Commonwealth African Assistance Plan, 1966.

"This map forms part of a Vegetation-Land Use Survey of South-western Kenya sponsored jointly by the East African Agriculture and Forestry Research Organization, the Directorate of Overseas Surveys, and the Kenya Ministry of Agriculture and Animal Husbandry."
Accompanied by: Vegetation and climate maps of South-western Kenya / C.G. Trapnell and M.A. Brunt. Surbiton, Surrey : Land Resources Development Centre, 1987. 9p.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain, Directorate of Overseas Surveys.
